<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 14:09:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登对以色列的未来有一个愿景。内塔尼亚胡不</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-reckless-stupidity-in-ignoring-the-biden-plan-for-a-new-middle-east/0000018d-f41d-da4e-adbf-f6bdec4d0000</link><description>一个超级大国为一个规模小得多、不对称的盟友制定并提供长期大战略，就像美国总统乔·拜登正在制定的新中东计划一样，这是史无前例的。以色列至少能做的就是给予该计划应有的关注</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 13:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-reckless-stupidity-in-ignoring-the-biden-plan-for-a-new-middle-east/0000018d-f41d-da4e-adbf-f6bdec4d0000</guid></item><item><title>“一秒钟就消失了”：以色列北部失踪的九岁女孩的搜寻工作仍在继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/vanished-in-a-second-search-continues-for-missing-nine-year-old-girl-in-israels-north/0000018d-f49c-da4e-adbf-f6bdc4a30000</link><description>海马诺特·卡绍（Haimanot Kassau）最后一次露面是在周日，安全摄像头没有看到她离开最后一次露面的吸收中心。警方在大批志愿者的协助下正在搜查周围的山区</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 12:51:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/vanished-in-a-second-search-continues-for-missing-nine-year-old-girl-in-israels-north/0000018d-f49c-da4e-adbf-f6bdc4a30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列导演的演讲并不反犹太主义。本来就是懦弱的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-directors-speech-wasnt-antisemitic-it-was-cowardly/0000018d-f473-da4e-adbf-f6fb44b80000</link><description>对于仇视以色列的人来说，以色列电影制片人尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕在柏林电影节的演讲是一份无价的礼物，他谈到了占领和种族隔离，但没有提及 10 月 7 日的大屠杀或人质。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 12:16:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israeli-directors-speech-wasnt-antisemitic-it-was-cowardly/0000018d-f473-da4e-adbf-f6fb44b80000</guid></item><item><title>在耶路撒冷发现的罕见腓尼基宝石。但这与所罗门王有关吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-29/ty-article/rare-phoenician-pendant-found-in-jerusalem-but-is-it-linked-to-king-solomon/0000018d-f47e-d401-a3dd-fd7ef50c0000</link><description>保守派学者声称金耳环证明了圣经中腓尼基人出现在所罗门宫廷的故事。但怀疑论者回应，年代测定完全错误，宝石可能已被交易</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 12:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-02-29/ty-article/rare-phoenician-pendant-found-in-jerusalem-but-is-it-linked-to-king-solomon/0000018d-f47e-d401-a3dd-fd7ef50c0000</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，美国年轻人现在比长辈更有可能相信对犹太人的负面刻板印象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-more-likely-than-their-elders-to-believe-negative-stereotypes-about-jews/0000018d-f419-dd0a-afcf-ffdf8a5a0000</link><description>ADL 的一项新调查询问受访者是否认为犹太人对以色列比对美国更忠诚，他们是否认为犹太人比其他人更愿意利用不正当手段来获得他们想要的东西，以及他们是否认为犹太人对华尔街有太多控制权</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-more-likely-than-their-elders-to-believe-negative-stereotypes-about-jews/0000018d-f419-dd0a-afcf-ffdf8a5a0000</guid></item><item><title>CNN：拜登政府担心，如果外交失败，以色列可能在春末入侵黎巴嫩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/report-u-s-concerned-israel-may-invade-lebanon-in-late-spring-if-diplomacy-fails/0000018d-f3f7-d7f4-a3dd-f7ff42ce0000</link><description>拜登政府一名高级官员表示，“我们的行动假设以色列将在未来几个月内采取军事行动”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 10:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/report-u-s-concerned-israel-may-invade-lebanon-in-late-spring-if-diplomacy-fails/0000018d-f3f7-d7f4-a3dd-f7ff42ce0000</guid></item><item><title>当局称，30,000 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙被杀，其中包括 12,500 名儿童和青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/30-000-palestinians-killed-in-gaza-hamas-says-as-hunger-and-despair-spread/0000018d-ef7f-d1e0-a1dd-ffff13100000</link><description>然而，这些数字并未代表死亡总数，因为据信整个加沙地带约有 8,000 名失踪者被埋在废墟下。无国界医生组织表示，“心理伤害导致五岁的孩子告诉我们他们宁愿死”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/30-000-palestinians-killed-in-gaza-hamas-says-as-hunger-and-despair-spread/0000018d-ef7f-d1e0-a1dd-ffff13100000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全官员：部长们泄露加沙北部援助计划损害人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/security-officials-right-wing-ministers-leaking-north-gaza-aid-plan-harms-hostage-talks/0000018d-f3e2-d401-a3dd-fbfa1db90000</link><description>向加沙地带北部提供援助的决定本可以用作人质释放谈判的筹码，但在极右翼部长就该行动发表公开声明后，这一决定可能不再可行</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 09:35:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/security-officials-right-wing-ministers-leaking-north-gaza-aid-plan-harms-hostage-talks/0000018d-f3e2-d401-a3dd-fbfa1db90000</guid></item><item><title>着眼未来的战斗，以色列自由派在昏昏欲睡的地方选举中保持警惕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/eying-future-battles-israeli-liberals-kept-their-powder-dry-in-sleepy-local-elections/0000018d-f129-dd8a-a5af-f97faaac0000</link><description>在本周的市政选举中，世俗、左倾的以色列人的结果好坏参半，但现在焦点转移到下一场重大战役：迫使提前选举、人质的命运和极端正统派选秀</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/eying-future-battles-israeli-liberals-kept-their-powder-dry-in-sleepy-local-elections/0000018d-f129-dd8a-a5af-f97faaac0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯警告加沙“大屠杀”可能会破坏与以色列的人质、停火谈判；据报道超过100人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article-live/syria-says-it-thwarted-israeli-strike-in-damascus/0000018d-f2cd-d7f4-a3dd-f6cd4e760000</link><description>以色列军队在分发食品期间向加沙人群开火，称军队面临“暴力拥挤”风险 ■ 当局报告，自战争开始以来，加沙死亡人数已超过 30,000 人 ■ 以色列国防军称，有 10 枚火箭弹袭击了以色列北部 ■ 叙利亚称，它挫败了以色列对大马士革的袭击 ■英国增加对犹太社区的安全资助</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 03:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article-live/syria-says-it-thwarted-israeli-strike-in-damascus/0000018d-f2cd-d7f4-a3dd-f6cd4e760000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的极右翼政党未能实现市长目标，但在地方议会中站稳了脚跟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-party-falls-short-in-mayoral-races-but-gets-foothold-on-local-councils/0000018d-f127-dd8a-a5af-f97f36ae0000</link><description>在右倾社区和混合城镇，代表本格维尔政党的候选人未能赢得选票，该党的市长候选人在竞选中也处于边缘人物，但该极端主义政党现在首次在一些地方议会中拥有席位</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 23:31:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-29/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-party-falls-short-in-mayoral-races-but-gets-foothold-on-local-councils/0000018d-f127-dd8a-a5af-f97f36ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方签署命令，可能将约旦河西岸前哨基地转变为主要城市定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-signs-order-that-could-turn-west-bank-outpost-into-major-urban-settlement/0000018d-f16b-d7f4-a3dd-f76f6abe0000</link><description>该命令是继去年内阁决定授权在西岸建立 10 个前哨基地之后发出的。 “立即和平”谴责“对以色列和两国解决方案的严重打击”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-military-signs-order-that-could-turn-west-bank-outpost-into-major-urban-settlement/0000018d-f16b-d7f4-a3dd-f76f6abe0000</guid></item><item><title>自本格维尔上任以来，以色列警方在会议上不再讨论犹太恐怖主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/police-withhold-discussing-jewish-terrorism-at-meetings-since-ben-gvir-took-office/0000018d-f16b-da4e-a18d-fdeb02c60000</link><description>关于安全局势的每周会议不再包括警察情报部门对犹太人民族主义犯罪问题的审查。消息人士称，提出这一问题的辛贝特官员遭到了极右翼部长的谴责和敲桌子。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/police-withhold-discussing-jewish-terrorism-at-meetings-since-ben-gvir-took-office/0000018d-f16b-da4e-a18d-fdeb02c60000</guid></item><item><title>没有人告诉以色列人与真主党的战争到底会是什么样子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/no-one-is-telling-israelis-what-a-war-with-hezbollah-would-really-be-like/0000018d-f104-dd0a-afcf-ffd697580000</link><description>对民用基础设施的毁灭性攻击、地区溢出效应、缺乏美国对战争的支持——如果与真主党开辟第二战线，这就是严峻的现实</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 21:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/no-one-is-telling-israelis-what-a-war-with-hezbollah-would-really-be-like/0000018d-f104-dd0a-afcf-ffd697580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前财政部长 Avraham Shochat 去世，享年 87 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/former-israeli-finance-minister-avraham-shochat-dies-at-87/0000018d-f14b-d401-a3dd-f95b811d0000</link><description>这位工党政客曾担任阿拉德市市长 22 年，并担任议会议员 14 年。肖查特与伊扎克·拉宾关系密切，负责《奥斯陆协议》的经济方面</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/former-israeli-finance-minister-avraham-shochat-dies-at-87/0000018d-f14b-d401-a3dd-f95b811d0000</guid></item><item><title>前总理奥尔默特：“内塔尼亚胡的过度自信和傲慢导致了 10 月 7 日的事件”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-28/ty-article-podcast/netanyahus-overconfidence-and-arrogance-led-to-oct-7-former-pm-olmert/0000018d-f07b-dd8a-a5af-f87ffc090000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-28/ty-article-podcast/netanyahus-overconfidence-and-arrogance-led-to-oct-7-former-pm-olmert/0000018d-f07b-dd8a-a5af-f87ffc090000</guid></item><item><title>超过 50 名国际广播记者呼吁埃及和以色列允许“自由和不受限制”进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/over-50-intl-broadcast-journalists-call-on-egypt-and-israel-to-allow-free-access-to-gaza/0000018d-f0a9-d7f4-a3dd-f6ad7cdf0000</link><description>这封信由美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）和英国广播公司（BBC）等媒体的资深记者签署，呼吁以色列允许外国记者进入加沙，而不必“嵌入”以色列国防军，并呼吁埃及允许进入拉法口岸。它还要求以色列尊重当地巴勒斯坦记者的安全</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/over-50-intl-broadcast-journalists-call-on-egypt-and-israel-to-allow-free-access-to-gaza/0000018d-f0a9-d7f4-a3dd-f6ad7cdf0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 145 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-145/0000018d-f089-d7f4-a3dd-f68d05d70000</link><description>哈马斯政治局主席哈尼亚表示，该组织在释放人质/停火谈判方面持灵活态度，但已做好继续战斗的准备，并呼吁穆斯林在斋月第一天加固阿克萨清真寺。 ■ 以色列国防军：160 包人道主义援助物资空投到叙利亚加沙南部 ■ 哈马斯和法塔赫代表团将于周四在莫斯科会面，讨论组建统一的巴勒斯坦政府 ■ 战争结束 145 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 17:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-145/0000018d-f089-d7f4-a3dd-f68d05d70000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦外长表示与哈马斯关于统一政府的谈判预计不会出现“奇迹”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/palestinian-seminister-no-miracles-expected-at-talks-on-unified-government/0000018d-f04e-dd8a-a5af-f87ecf160000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总理穆罕默德·什塔耶辞职几天后，哈马斯和法塔赫的代表定于周四在莫斯科举行会谈</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-28/ty-article/palestinian-seminister-no-miracles-expected-at-talks-on-unified-government/0000018d-f04e-dd8a-a5af-f87ecf160000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 解释道：美国强大且分裂的亲以色列游说团体的内幕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aipac-explained-the-inside-story-of-americas-powerful-and-divisive-pro-israel-lobby/0000018d-e4ac-d972-a5bf-efaf96c60000</link><description>美国以色列公共事务委员会与美国总统和政客发生冲突、纵容、针对和支持，使以色列成为一个日益党派化的问题。以下是您需要了解的有关 AIPAC 的信息，这是一个令人尊敬、令人恐惧和谩骂的游说和政治筹款组织，准备在 2024 年的选举中发挥巨大作用</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:06:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/aipac-explained-the-inside-story-of-americas-powerful-and-divisive-pro-israel-lobby/0000018d-e4ac-d972-a5bf-efaf96c60000</guid></item></channel></rss>